In this video, i was playing with Random Players who were under the impression id never played zombies before! I have the full game recorded and will be using it for 'Black Ops Zombies: The Noob' . 
So i was expecting these guys to troll me and not help me but they actually gave me a lot of awesome advise if i was a starting new player on zombies!

Whilst we played they got in to some trickey situations and when i was the last one left id clutch the round and impress these guys as they thought id never played before, and here is their reaction!
